data.title: New dad Owen Wilson breaks the weird celebrity baby naming trend
data.meta_description: Little Fockers actor gives his newborn son a surprisingly normal name…
data.text:
Owen Wilson shocked the world with the unexpected news that he was to become a dad for the first time earlier this month, and now the actor has shocked us all again – by giving his newborn son a normal name!

Advertisement

Shunning the weird and wonderful monikers that celebrities usually go for, the 42-year-old choose to name his week- old son, Robert Ford.

Despite rumours claiming that Owen had chosen the name Ford Linton, the actor and his partner Jade Duell actually decided on a more traditional and, dare we say ordinary, name.
